  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a small and relaxing game in which you have to find objects made with pixels, within levels made with those same objects! Each level is unique, adorable and procedural, allowing you to play your favorite levels infinitely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876920/extras/898c09810c45ccc590ad9afd06736e84.poster.avif?t=1727708891\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876920/extras/898c09810c45ccc590ad9afd06736e84.webm?t=1727708891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876920/extras/898c09810c45ccc590ad9afd06736e84.mp4?t=1727708891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore each of the beautiful levels, looking for all kinds of objects related to the theme. Each level you complete unlocks new challenges and items to find, as well as a daily challenge full of unique variety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you find all the objects and get the 3 stars in each level?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876920/extras/6c1c399a1e8a54beb6c6a79d5488b925.poster.avif?t=1727708891\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876920/extras/6c1c399a1e8a54beb6c6a79d5488b925.webm?t=1727708891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876920/extras/6c1c399a1e8a54beb6c6a79d5488b925.mp4?t=1727708891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Characteristics</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colorful and varied theme design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thematic levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zoom, hints and rechargeable lives </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast levels, perfect for short games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful objects in 1 bit Pixelart</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for practicing vocabulary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily Challenge with hundreds of designs and objects to find</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876920/extras/ed54e7f1ac719f12a75d8620821de3b5.poster.avif?t=1727708891\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876920/extras/ed54e7f1ac719f12a75d8620821de3b5.webm?t=1727708891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876920/extras/ed54e7f1ac719f12a75d8620821de3b5.mp4?t=1727708891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
